<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a108d9b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s3003"><num value="3003">§ 3003.</num><heading> Acceptance of interstate off-track wager</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No person may accept an interstate off-track wager except as provided in this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a108d9c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/515/s4">Pub. L. 95–515, § 4</ref>, <date date="1978-10-25">Oct. 25, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/1813">92 Stat. 1813</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
